- Log reasons for lost deals — this data is gold.
- Identify average deal value per lead channel.
{% elif dimension in ['Operations', 'العمليات'] or 'oper' in dimension.lower() or 'عمليات' in dimension %}
- Document your most repeated process in 5 steps.
- Identify the step that takes the longest — that is your first improvement point.
- Create a simple checklist for that process.
{% elif dimension in ['Customer Health', 'صحة العملاء'] or 'customer' in dimension.lower() or 'عملاء' in dimension %}
- Reach out to 3 current clients this week to check satisfaction.
- Log the last contact date for each client — silence for 30+ days signals churn risk.
- Ask a satisfied client for a written testimonial.
{% else %}
- Assign one person as owner of this dimension in your organisation.
- Set one measurable goal for this month in this dimension.
- Review current state against the applicable sector benchmark.
{% endif %}

